snippet.title: Project Zero - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Project Zero brings an intense, fast-paced and fun first-person shooter experience for up to 16 players per match. With six different game modes to choose from, including Team Death Match, Free For All, Capture The Flag, Gun Game, Elimination, and Bomb Defusal, players can compete in a variety of modes that cater to different playstyles.

Wishlist Project Zero now on Steam.
